        Details:

        'Function : CompareTwoUpdatesPerf()
        'Functionality : The performance version of Change management to Compare Tables with 2 Transactions

        ' From Chck Status Dialog -> << Changes Since Import>>
        ' strReportType = "ChangesAfterImport"
        '
        'From Table Histroy WorkSheet (with CheckBoxes)
        ' << Show Table at Selected Time >>
        ' strReportType = "CompleteTableWithChanges"
        '
        '
        ' << Compare Two updates >>
        ' strReportType = "CompareTwoUpdates"
